The paper deals with natural language understanding, specifically slot filling and intent detection, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The proposed model is a neural network, which is a common tool in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of capsule networks is a relatively new and innovative approach, which could also fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) or computer vision (cs.CV) due to their ability to capture spatial relationships.
